lets do Hotel Hafnia for the first day

Sure, Hotel Hafnia is a great choice for your first day in Tórshavn. It's centrally located, so you'll be close to all the action. It also has a restaurant, a bar, and a sauna, so you can relax after a long day of exploring. 
Hotel Hafnia Torshavn Faroe IslandsOpens in a new window
www.booking.com
Hotel Hafnia Torshavn Faroe Islands

Here are some of the pros and cons of staying at Hotel Hafnia:

Pros:

Centrally located
Restaurant, bar, and sauna
Free WiFi
Pet friendly
24-hour front desk
Cons:

Can be noisy at night
Rooms can be small
No elevator
Overall, I think Hotel Hafnia is a great choice for your first day in Tórshavn. It's a good value for the price, and it has everything you need for a comfortable stay.

